OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly clear
OL,6,Fthis evening in the north with some
OL,7,Ffrost forming, and central and
OL,8,Fnortheastern parts of Scotland will
OL,9,Fremain chilly overnight. Elsewhere
OL,10,Fcloud will increase from the south.
OL,11,FLight rain developing Northern Ireland
OL,12,Fand southwest Scotland. Some fog
OL,13,Fpatches.
OL,14,
OL,15,CWednesday:FIt will be rather cloudy
OL,16,Fand breezy across Scotland and
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland tomorrow with patchy
OL,18,Frain. Elsewhere low cloud and fog
OL,19,Fslowly lifting to give some pleasantly
OL,20,Fwarm sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
